metadata.name: Queen of Dreams
metadata.description:
Every night when you look up at the sky and make a wish at the shooting stars, Linda hears you. 
But she's not alone. The queen of dreams has a helper - her three-eyed rabbit. Together they create new stars, so that everyone can make and make their wish come true. 
Linda and her rabbit are here to keep people dreaming and believing in good. 
They believe that dreams lead to the realization of grand goals.
